Legendary Secret Agent :     Replaces Legendary Pointman COM, Vladof COM. Buff cooldown rate, weapon damage and grants ammo regen.
Buff the following skills : 1) Sentry, 2) Expertise, 3) Impact, 4) Battlefront, 5) Grit.

Legendary Soldier :          Replaces the skill Healthy by Ranger.

Legendary Rifleman : Replaces Legendary Ranger, Jakobs COM. Same buffs and skills as a classic Rifleman COM.
In addition boosts Duty calls and Ranger skills.

---- Note : If you already have said class mod in your inventory, it will not apply the manufacturer changes.
           In this case you can re-farm one or use gib to update the manufacturer,
           Example : For the Legendary Rifleman COM, 1) open Gibbed -> 2) select your save file -> 3) click on your legendary Ranger COM -> 4) manufacturer : GD_Manufacturers.Manufacturers.Anshin -> replace Anshin by Jakobs -> 5) save.
